+- `src/js/03-sheet-basics.js` — `showTab()` now calls `WM.rescale('sheet')`
+- `src/js/14-window-manager.js` — new public `WM.rescale(id)`
+- `PROJECT.md` — §3.10, §5, §7 updated to match
+- `UX-AUDIT.md` — this document (new)
